"Boy Is a Bottom" is a song by American singer and drag queen Willam Belli, featuring Detox and Vicky Vox (DWV). The song was released to coincide with the fifth season premiere of RuPaul's Drag Race. The original music video went viral. As of July 2014, the clip has been viewed over 19 million times since uploaded to YouTube on 28 January 2013.
On 13 January 2015, Willam released a Spanish version of the song, called "Es Una Pasiva".
